hopobject.body: Could I have , please? buy ventolin nebules online uk With their backs to the wall, Jamaat and its allies sounded an old alarm bell again, claiming Islam itself was under attack. The trials were branded as attacks on Islam and Muslims. Ironically, they were helped in this regard by huge demonstrations at a place in Dhaka called Shahbag, demanding the death penalty for Jamaat leader Abdul Qader Mollah after he was given life imprisonment.
